title: The Avalanches - When I Met You [Gimix] CD + covers
description:
This bootleg CD has become rather rare as of lately (I've seen copies on Amazon fetching $100USD+). So to combat this crazy pricing, I've decided to upload a personal copy of mine complete with full artwork. So you can make it look just like the real thing and annoy the price gougers to boot ;)

CD was ripped using Exact Audio Copy in high quality MP3 format. If I get enough requests, I will try to upload it in different formats.

CD Description:
When I Met You is a 2 Many DJs-style mix by Australia's The Avalanches. Fans of The Avalanches will do well to seek this out. It is well put together and a lot of fun. This mix-n-mash collection features 42 tracks from Madonna, Fleetwood Mac, De La Soul, The Avalanches, Blowfly, ODB, Kid Creole & The Coconuts, Cyndi Lauper, The Smiths, Men At Work, Hall & Oates, Fatboy Slim and many others.
